334
00:23:43.320 --> 00:23:45.600
Her laptop's there.

335
00:23:45.600 --> 00:23:48.000
Those are her reading glasses.
so when I saw those.

336
00:23:48.000 --> 00:23:50.720
I thought that's a good thing
